        <h4>Your Unexamined Beliefs</h4>
        <p>Identify a belief you hold strongly—about politics, morality, religion, or your own field of expertise. Try to articulate exactly what you believe and why. Then ask yourself Socratic questions: What do I mean by these key terms? What's my evidence? What would change my mind? Write down where you get stuck.</p>
